{# templates/email_base.j2 #}
{% if mood == 'Angry' %}
Dear {{ user_name | default('Customer') }},

Thank you for reaching out to us. I completely understand your frustration regarding this issue, and I want to assure you that resolving this is my top priority.
{% elif mood == 'Happy' %}
Hi {{ user_name | default('Customer') }},

Thank you so much for your kind words! We are thrilled to hear from you.
{% elif mood == 'Urgent' %}
Dear {{ user_name | default('Customer') }},

Thank you for contacting us. I understand this is an urgent matter, and I am reviewing your request immediately.
{% else %}
Dear {{ user_name | default('Customer') }},

Thank you for contacting JUNO Support. We appreciate the opportunity to assist you.
{% endif %}

{% block content %}{% endblock %}

{% if mood == 'Angry' or mood == 'Urgent' %}
Sincerely,

**The JUNO Priority Support Team**
{% else %}
Best regards,

**The JUNO Support Team**
{% endif %}
